summary: An ordinance accepting deeds form Mrs. Guro Locken as administratrix of the Estate of John Locken, deceased, to the City of Seattle; from Bertha A. Vandyke and D.E. Vandyke, her husband, to the City of Seattle; and from J.E. Abramson and Louise Abramson, husband and wife, to the City of Seattle; and laying off Dawson Street.
